ntsb3110txt-1-5-5-0-2 Information from the flight data recorder indicated that during descent from flight level 290, an elevator oscillation occurred. 
ntsb3110txt-1-5-5-0-3 The #1 and #2 engines were shut down due to high turbine gas temperatures. 
ntsb3110txt-1-5-5-0-4 The #2 engine was restarted before making an emergency landing at the Des Moines Airport. 
